# Spec Edit Safety Rule

Requirement specifications under `spec/requirements/` are user-owned.

- Do not change files in `spec/requirements/` unless explicitly requested in the current task.
- If implementation implies a spec update, ask first unless the user asked for spec editing.
- Treat user wording as source of truth and avoid silent rewrites.
